name: ANYTHING YOU SAY OR DO CAN AND WILL BE USED AGAINST YOU IN A TARGETED ADVERTISEMENT
description: From the "Think Privacy" series of motivational privacy posters first launched in 2016 at the New Museum Store in NYC as part of the Privacy Gift Shop. Created as a total edition of 100. The first 50 editions were screenprinted. The second half are screenminted. Add 50 to the NFT edition number for the total adjusted edition number. Format: A2, 300PI, PNG, 7016 x 4961 pixels.
